color: #0000ff; font-size: 110%;\"><b>MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC SINH KH\u00d4NG HI\u1ec2U B\u00c0I<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 110%;\"><b>\u00a0 Hotline: 0962.005.996 &#8211; 0987.005.996<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<b>Gia s\u01b0 B\u00ecnh<\/b> <b>Minh<\/b> chuy\u00ean gia s\u01b0 h\u00f3a t\u1eeb 8 \u0111\u1ebfb 12, cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m h\u00f3a t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<b>,<\/b> gi\u00fap l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u0103n b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh y\u1ebfu, n\u00e2ng cao ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh kh\u00e1 gi\u1ecfi.<i> G<\/i>i\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh h\u1ecdc ch\u1eafc, hi\u1ec3u s\u00e2u, n\u00e2ng cao t\u01b0 duy\u00a0m\u00f4n <i>Ho\u00e1<\/i>\u00a0H\u1ecdc &#8211; v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecdc th\u1eed 02 bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 cam k\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gia s\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"I_%E2%80%93_GIA_SU_TRI_VIET_CUNG_CAP_GIA_SU_HOA_GIOI_O_HA_NOI\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\">I &#8211;\u00a0 GIA S\u01af B\u00ccNH M\u00ccNH CUNG C\u1ea4P GIA S\u01af HO\u00c1 GI\u1eceI \u1ede H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Nh\u1eb1m\u00a0gi\u00fap cha m\u1eb9\u00a0y\u00ean t\u00e2m\u00a0cho vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp\u00a0c\u1ee7a con,\u00a0Gia S\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t cung c\u1ea5p gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, sinh vi\u00ean\u00a0gi\u1ecfi d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m m\u00f4n H\u00f3a H\u1ecdc l\u1edbp 8, 9, 10, 11, 12, gia s\u01b0 luy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u1edf m\u1ecdi qu\u1eadn, huy\u1ec7n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n TP H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 Quy tr\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 Ho\u00e1 nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t khi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n t\u1eeb k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng m\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ebfn ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n Ho\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn gia \u0111\u00ecnh bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><em><strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"emoji\" role=\"img\" draggable=\"false\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/12.0.0-1\/svg\/1f539.svg\" alt=\"????\" \/> Nh\u1eefng sinh vi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u00ean kh\u1ed1i A, B nh\u01b0 \u0110H B\u00e1ch Khoa, \u0110H Y H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, Kinh T\u1ebf , \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c Gia, khoa S\u01b0 Ph\u1ea1m Ho\u00e1\u2026.<\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"emoji\" role=\"img\" draggable=\"false\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/12.0.0-1\/svg\/1f539.svg\" alt=\"????\" \/> C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m thi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o \u0110H &gt; 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"emoji\" role=\"img\" draggable=\"false\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/12.0.0-1\/svg\/1f539.svg\" alt=\"????\" \/> Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u0111ang c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"emoji\" role=\"img\" draggable=\"false\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/12.0.0-1\/svg\/1f539.svg\" alt=\"????\" \/> Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean \u0111ang d\u1ea1y t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m luy\u1ec7n thi \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, vi\u1ec7n h\u00e0n l\u00e2m<\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><em><strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"emoji\" role=\"img\" draggable=\"false\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/12.0.0-1\/svg\/1f539.svg\" alt=\"????\" \/> Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m ho\u00e1 \u0111ang d\u1ea1y t\u1ef1 do gia s\u01b0.<\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1578\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1578\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1578\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-hoa-300x169.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-hoa-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-hoa-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-hoa-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Gia-su-hoa.png 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1578\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><em>Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 Ho\u00e1 gi\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 gia s\u01b0 Ho\u00e1 c\u1ee7a trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec1u\u00a0c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0 <\/span>gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y m\u00f4n H\u00f3a, t\u00e2m huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 y\u00eau ngh\u1ec1.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"II_%E2%80%93_BANG_GIA_HOC_PHI_GIA_SU_MON_HOA_TAI_HA_NOI_2020\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\">II &#8211; B\u1ea2NG GI\u00c1, H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af M\u00d4N HO\u00c1 T\u1ea0I H\u00c0 N\u1ed8I 2020<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><h2 id=\"tablepress-18-name\" class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-18\">H\u1eccC PH\u00cd - GIA S\u01af HO\u00c1 T\u1ea0I NH\u00c0<\/h2>\n\n<table id=\"tablepress-18\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-18 tbody-has-connected-cells\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-18-name\">\n<tbody class=\"row-striping row-hover\">\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n\t<td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"column-1\">L\u1edaP H\u1eccC<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">SINH VI\u00caN<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">GI\u00c1O VI\u00caN<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\n\t<td class=\"column-2\">1 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">2 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">1 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">2 H\u1ecdc sinh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">L\u1edbp 8<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">130.000 \u2013 150.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">180.000 \u2013 200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\"> 250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 \u2013 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 9<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">180.000 - 200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\"> 250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">300.000 - 350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">C\u1ea5p 3<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 180.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 300.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">350.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u00d4n thi \u0110\u1ea1i H\u1ecdc<\/td><td class=\"column-2\">150.000 - 200.000<\/td><td class=\"column-3\">220.000 - 250.000<\/td><td class=\"column-4\">250.000 - 350.000<\/td><td class=\"column-5\">350.000 - 400.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\n\t<td class=\"column-1\">\u00d4n thi h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi, HS chuy\u00ean<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-2\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"column-4\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<!-- #tablepress-18 from cache -->\n<strong>Xem ngay:<\/strong><i><br \/>\n&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;<\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/hoc-phi-bang-gia-gia-su-tai-nha-hn-mon-toan-anh-van-hoa-ly\/\">H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/a><\/span> t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n \u1edf HN- M\u00f4n To\u00e1n, Anh, V\u0103n, Ho\u00e1, L\u00fd<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">[TOP1] <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top1-gia-su-van-ha-noi-bang-gia-mon-van-moi-nhat-2018\/\">Gia s\u01b0 V\u0103n<\/a><\/span> H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u2013 B\u00ed k\u00edp l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gia s\u01b0 v\u0103n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c m\u1eb9 chia s\u1ebb r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;\u00a0[B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1] 500+ <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/bang-gia-500-gia-su-mon-toan-gioi-tu-lop-1-12-o-ha-noi\/\">Gia s\u01b0 m\u00f4n To\u00e1n<\/a><\/span> gi\u1ecfi \u2013 T\u1eeb l\u1edbp 1-12 \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i &#8211; Nh\u1eadn ngay 02 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"III_%E2%80%93_02_BUOI_DAY_THU_%E2%80%93_TAI_SAO_GIA_SU_NEN_DAY_THU\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\">III &#8211; 02 BU\u1ed4I D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec &#8211; T\u1ea0I SAO GIA S\u01af N\u00caN D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><b>T\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho con kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n d\u1ec5. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ph\u1ee5 huynh t\u00ecm t\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 than r\u1eb1ng &#8220;anh, ch\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u gia s\u01b0 r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p gia s\u01b0 n\u00e0o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a con&#8221;.<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"31_%E2%80%93_Vi_sao_phu_huynh_can_gia_su_day_thu\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 100%;\"><b>3.1 &#8211; V\u00ec sao ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u1ea7n gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y th\u1eed?<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><em><strong>Gi\u00fap gia \u0111\u00ecnh y\u00ean t\u00e2m h\u01a1n<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn ph\u1ee5 huynh lu\u00f4n b\u0103n kho\u0103n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gia s\u01b0 khi c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay m\u1ecdc l\u00ean \u00a0kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian d\u1ea1y th\u1eed 2 bu\u1ed5i, ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1o \u00e1n, ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1\u00a0 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a con.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><em><strong>\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 v\u00e0 con<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">Qua 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed, ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi con v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 nh\u1eadn gia s\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1579\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1579\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1579\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/hoc-thu-gia-su-tai-nha-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/hoc-thu-gia-su-tai-nha-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/hoc-thu-gia-su-tai-nha.png 650w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1579\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><em>H\u1ecdc th\u1eed 02 bu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 Ho\u00e1 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4 class=\"p4\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"32_%E2%80%93_Quy_dinh_hoc_thu\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 100%;\"><b>3.2 &#8211; Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecdc th\u1eed<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">&#8211;\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0 \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n<b>\u00a0t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 <\/b>nh\u01b0 \u00fd, trong ph\u1ea1m vi 2 bu\u1ed5i:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"> \u00a0\u00a0N\u1ebfu gia \u0111\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gia s\u01b0, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thay gia s\u01b0. Ho\u1eb7c h\u1ee7y h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i thanh to\u00e1n b\u1ea5t k\u00ec kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"> \u00a0\u00a0Sau 2 bu\u1ed5i, ph\u1ee5 huynh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eddi gia s\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m cho con m\u00ecnh. Ph\u1ee5 huynh s\u1ebd thanh to\u00e1n ph\u00ed cho gia s\u01b0 ngay v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng (bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 2 bu\u1ed5i d\u1ea1y th\u1eed).<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">&gt;&gt;&gt; Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y th\u1eed s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5 huynh, h\u1ecdc sinh y\u00ean t\u00e2m h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t c\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u00a0con m\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; font-size: 100%;\">Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t, chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 sau m\u1ea5y bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f3 con \u00a0ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t t\u1ed1t ngay. V\u00ec \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n &#8221; Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y hai m\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&#8221; \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh m\u1ea5t ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, l\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc&#8230;\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IV_%E2%80%93_CAM_KET_CUA_TRUNG_TAM_GIA_SU_TRI_VIET\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\">IV &#8211; CAM K\u1ebeT C\u1ee6A TRUNG T\u00c2M GIA S\u01af TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul class=\"ul2\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">T\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd<\/span><\/em><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><b><\/b>Th\u00f4ng tin gia s\u01b0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 Gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd, b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p, CMND, th\u1ebb SV, GV<\/span><\/em><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><b><\/b>Gia s\u01b0 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y<\/span><\/em><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><b><\/b>T\u1eadn t\u00e2m, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u1ea1y h\u1ebft b\u00e0i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft gi\u1edd.<\/span><\/em><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><b><\/b>D\u1ea1y \u0111\u00fang ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda h\u1ecdc sinh &amp; gia \u0111\u00ecnh<\/span><\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">=&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">TOP 3000+<\/span> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-3000-gia-su-tieng-anh-tai-nha-tang-hieu-qua-gap-5-lan\/\">gia s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfng anh<\/a><\/span> <span style=\"color: #000000;\">t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u2013 T\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 g\u1ea5p 5 l\u1ea7n<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-500-gia-su-vat-ly-gia-su-su-pham-gioi\/\">Gia s\u01b0 L\u00fd<\/a><\/span> &#8211; Gia s\u01b0 S\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m gi\u1ecfi, chuy\u00ean L\u00fd &#8211; H\u1ecdc th\u1eed 2 bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\">=&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n con nh\u1ecf \u0111ang \u1edf b\u1eadc ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc, h\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o ngay: <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/top-1-gia-su-tieu-hoc-su-pham-hoc-phi-chi-tu-100k\/\"><b>gia<\/b> <b>s\u01b0<\/b> <b>ti\u1ec3u<\/b> <b>h\u1ecdc <\/b><\/a><\/span>t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 &#8211; H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 50k\/h &#8211; Gi\u00fap con t\u1eadp chung, cam k\u1ebft ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 sau 8 bu\u1ed5i<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 100%;\"><i>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #d83131;\"><strong>TRUNG T\u00c2M\u00a0GIA S\u01af\u00a0TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 1: N03, S\u1ed1 38-40 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u00fd Ki\u00ean, C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 2: S\u1ed1 263 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh, ph\u01b0\u1eddng Xu\u00e2n H\u00f2a, t\u1ec9nh Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd, Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li2\">\n<p class=\"footer-text\"><strong>C\u01a1 s\u1edf 3: 479 L\u0129nh Nam, Ho\u00e0ng Mai, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p2\"><b>==&gt; Hotline (24\/7): 0962.005.996 \u2013 0987.005.996\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GIA S\u01af HO\u00c1 GI\u1eceI &#8211; \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC S\u01af PH\u1ea0M, \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC Y, NGO\u1ea0I TH\u01af\u01a0NG D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC SINH KH\u00d4NG HI\u1ec2U [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1702,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[480,493,494,495],"tags":[415,414,413,344,417,418,419,343,416,420],"class_list":["post-1576","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-gia-su-mon-hoa-mb","category-gia-su-quan-ba-dinh-mb","category-gia-su-quan-cau-giay-mb","category-gia-su-quan-thanh-xuan-mb","tag-gia-su-day-hoa","tag-gia-su-day-hoa-gioi","tag-gia-su-day-kem-hoa","tag-gia-su-hoa","tag-gia-su-hoa-ha-noi","tag-gia-su-hoa-tai-ha-noi","tag-gia-su-hoa-tai-nha","tag-gia-su-mon-hoa","tag-gia-su-mon-hoa-tai-ha-noi","tag-tim-gia-